    Grocery Stores in Nariman Point, Mumbai

    Also referred to as retail stores, grocery stores serve the primary purpose of selling all types of food items and products that are classified as household utility. Over a certain span of time it has evolved and progressed to catering to the likes of individuals by staking on the shelves numerous personal care products. Practically each and every one of them gives you a wide choice in processed and packaged food while only a few of them give you an additional choice in purchasing fresh vegetables and fruits as well as ready to eat food items from the counter. The range of fast-moving consumer goods (FMCG)products displayed at these centers are wide and from across brands. From diary products, juices and other soft drinks to biscuits, tea, sugar and floor cleaners you can be sure to find all that you need. These shops are situated at various parts in the city thus becoming more accessible. A majority of them accept multiple modes of payment such as cash, debit and credit cards. Find the nearest grocery stores in Nariman Point, Mumbai.

    Get Groceries Delivered at your Doorstep! Contact the Nearest Grocery Stores in Nariman Point, Mumbai!

    There are times when getting out of the house or the busy routine to buy grocery seems next to impossible. At such times, getting grocery delivered at your doorstep sounds like a perfect hassle-free solution and time-saver. Grocery stores in Nariman Point, Mumbai these days offer a wide range of basic home utility products like food, kitchenware, toiletries as well as personal beauty products all under one roof. Hence buying grocery becomes convenient. Let us have a look at the different products offered by grocery stores in Nariman Point Mumbai.

    Grocery and Other Staples like dals and pulses, rice and rice products, flour, grains, sugar, salt, oil, ghee, etc.

    Dairy and Beverages including cheese and butter

    Frozen Food Products like peas, paneer, corn, etc.

    Packaged Food Products like biscuits, snacks, ketchup, pasta, ready to cook, sweets, pickle, etc.

    Home and Kitchen Products like detergents, fabric cleaners, utensil cleaners, napkins, kitchen tools, home utility, etc.

    Delivery Services

    Grocery shops Nariman Point, Mumbai has, are offering delivery services amidst the coronavirus lockdown. These services are offered during a specific time slot every day. Keeping safety and hygiene at priority all the grocery shops are taking all the necessary measures mentioned in the guidelines by the government as well as WHO to ensure safe grocery home delivery services. Moreover, as a safety measure, many stores are accepting only online payments for home delivery services. Also, note that since the situation is getting critical day by day most grocery shops can deliver only essential food products.

    Delivery Charges

    The delivery charges vary from one grocery store to the other while a majority don’t charge additional delivery charges. It is always best to inquire about the same with the respective Nariman Point, Mumbai grocery store.

    Frequently Asked Questions

    1. What are the different grocery items available at supermarkets near me?

    There are awide range of products categories available which include:

    Grocery and other staples

    Dairy and Beverages

    Frozen Food Products

    Packaged Food Products

    2. Do grocery stores accept bulk orders?

    Only essential food requirements are fulfilled. In case of bulk requirements, you need to place an order well in advance for the store to be able to make it available.

    3. Do these stores provide good quality products?

    Yes, all the grocery shops in Mumbai provide fresh and good quality products.

    4. Can defective/expired products be returned?

    In case of any manufacturing defect or quality issue, you can return the product to the store. They may either offer an exchange or refund, depending on the respective store.

    It is best to check the various modes of payment accepted with the respective grocery store in Mumbai.
